Job Details
Earn extra income as a Part Time Driver.BuDDys Drivers on Demand are looking for Part Time Drivers in Abu Dhabi.
If you are looking to earn extra income as a part time driver please answer the questions below.
1. Are you able to work in the evening after 6pm during the week?2. Are you able to work during the weekend?3. Do you have a valid UAE drivers license?4. Are you familiar with the different Areas of Abu Dhabi?5. Are you older than 25 years?6. Do you have your own vehicle?
Our drivers work in teams, there is a driver and a sweeper. If you know of someone who has a valid UAE drivers license and is able to work with you that is a bonus.
Great earning potential for the right candidate.Email us on buddysabudhabi@gmail.com if you are interested.
